{"tid":1312501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［我地唔好學黑警］連登仔一齊同記者朋友道歉好無？","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:16:06.000Z","uid":125219,"like":174,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"67cb6a3e73aaf4a7704aefb6cdd1741d13b3bd6b","tid":1312501,"uid":125219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:59:35.000Z","msg":"其實我係係想講掟野<br />\n今日有個記者係新運路比鐵通掟中訓左落地要比佢同行拖走<br />\n（警察係一行車線急促推進 示威者係另一行車線掟鐵通阻礙佢地）<br />\n包圍果4個便衣警既時候都有記者比遮掟中<br />\n<br />\n我唔係唔比大家掟野<br />\n但係唔該大家錫住記者<br />\n佢地係警察前線已經要冒住比狗推同打既風險<br />\n我唔想佢地仲要搶心後面中野<br />\n次次記者都行到好前<br />\n好專業<br />\n發揮佢地第四權既作用<br />\n所以大家唔該！<br />\n有記者係到咪撚掟野 掟又唔係掟得準<br />\n無記者係到先掟！ 掟準啲呀屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者朋友！ 對唔住呀！ 錫哂你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1ab891130331ee4038ca7f2316f155a3f20559","tid":1312501,"uid":125219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45134a9a3539765a88b70fc88344fa57007570a4","tid":1312501,"uid":125219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:01:05.000Z","msg":"I love 記者朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00aa5717905fdef1cb1659bf16a8f246a3a212fb","tid":1312501,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:01.000Z","msg":"對唔住呀亦多謝你地<br />\n辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf26e244891d837ee38fd6f501ded1adbd91bb7","tid":1312501,"uid":67461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0a8b67fa50717fc6489f4fba9dabddcccb4794d","tid":1312501,"uid":26212,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚掟到立場姐姐，我同你死過！"},{"pid":"651e99069a867bf999d87269d342cf40a06decca","tid":1312501,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"對唔住 多謝你地 辛苦你地 要